metadata.name: Ape Motor Club
metadata.description: AMC is a collection of 6,666 Ape motor NFTs with +250 traits based on Etheruem blockchain. The collection contains immersive features like The Metaverse Casino, Car showroom, Play to earn events, and various other in real life and Metaverse events! Furthermore we are backed with DOA which is a decentralised system that will allow the Metaverse to develop hand in hand with the NFTs, made by the community for the community.
